<title>USA: INTERVIEW - PPD acquisitions add research.</title>
<headline>INTERVIEW - PPD acquisitions add research.</headline>
<byline>Ransdell Pierson</byline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-05-29</dateline>
<text>
<p>Pharmaceutical Product Development Inc predicted it would significantly widen its client base by vaulting into the research arena with two new acquisitions announced earlier Thursday.</p>
<p>The company said its value as a contract service provider to the drug industry would be enhanced by acquiring SARCO Inc, a combinatorial chemistry company, and buying the GSX System of functional genomics.</p>
